  attackReactions:
  - Glup, glup! (Ouch, right in the gills!)
  - Glup! Glup! (My suit can take more than that!)
  - Glup, glup... (Rabid beasts bite way harder!)
  - Glup! (Hey! Watch the fins!)
  - Glup, glup? (You call that an attack?)
  - Glup... glup! (This armor was built for pressure!)
  - Glup, glup, glup! (Careful, buddy. Sharks bite back!)
  - Glup?! Glup! (Right on the helmet? Seriously?)
  - "Glup, glup... (I\u2019ve survived deeper waters than this.)"
